(54, 'elsewhere', 'eleganza', 'ELEGANZA', 'Ring Co., Ltd.', '493/2 Soi Navamintr 24, Navamintr Rd., Klongkum, Bungkum, Bangkok 10240 THAILAND', '+66 2379 3072 # 134', 'sale@eleganza-co.com', '+66 2731 6315', 'www.eleganza-co.com', 'https://facebook.com/EleganzaBag', 'https://www.instagram.com/eleganzalife/', '', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=1lyj43-OjkK8xtRSUVwDbv2Rbn7soDhAR', 'SS19', 'EH 101 : CC -  43, 45', 'Ring Company Limited is a Manufacturer and Exporter of Fashion and Classic Ladies Handbags,Wallets,Key Holders and other small leather goods.\n\n        “ Ring ”  offers the customers only the touch of high class quality leather products with the modern stylish design from the finest materials which we use from market and import from the overseas with the intention of producing the attractive, elaborate and quality leather goods.\n', 'Spring/ Summer 2019 Collection(114 Mipel2018)/Style2018\n\nEleganza SS 2019 features warm colours with an underlying lightness, which makes them feel richer and more luxurious. Earthy tones anchor the palette, ranging from the luminous yellow of Marigold to the tan brown of Roasted Pecan and the deeper hues of Iron Red and Wild Aubergine and these are offset by leafy and aquatic tones such as Rubber Plant, Filtered Aqua and Deep Water Navy.\n        These are colours that feel familiar,comforting and connecting, offering broad appeal acrossmarkets and categories.\n        The need to re-establish what local means to global economies and invest in community-driven creative collaborations underpins this essential and responsible direction. Inspiration comes from local but globally hit story, naturally sourced materials, heritage craft and time-proven techniques, which are made relevant with a modern twist.\n', 1, '2018-10-13 13:09:30', NULL),
(55, 'spectacle', 'triple-p-paphonphat', 'T R I P L E - P  PAPHONPHAT', 'S.T. Sea Star Leather Co., Ltd.', '44/48 Moo 11, Bangkhuntian, Chomthong, Bangkok 10150 THAILAND', '+668 5486 5885', 'triple.p.bag@gmail.com', '', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/triple.p.bag', 'https://www.instagram.com/triple.p.bag/', '@mdg3428b', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=1vf1Yqp31pX3URT1pKRyRsJjEQJK7vOn-', 'SS19 - Arrow II', 'EH 100 : AA -  43, 45', 'T R I P L E - P  PAPHONPHAT  was founded with a vision to empower women to express themselves freely through fashion. The brand pushes the creative of handbag by modern graphic fashion that to make women look differently. \nT R I P L E - P  PAPHONPHAT was accessories brand name from Thailand. The Brand designed and produced products from exotic leather (main stingray leather). They use very special technical to mix stingray and cow leather in geometric graphic style. These is our Identity design of brand to made new look of Stingray hand bag \n     T R I P L E - P  PAPHONPHAT launched on 2016 .We have small shop Bangkok. And we sale product almost in online shop.\n', 'ARROW II Collection is continue collection from ARROW I in AW2018 Collection. This collection use our logo signature to make shape of bag. That is look so stronger and difference from another bag. All bag in this collection have special function.', 1, '2018-10-13 13:09:30', NULL),
(56, 'elsewhere', 'ador-n-adorn', 'ADOR N ADORN', 'Sabai-D Design Studio Co., Ltd.', '164 Sukhonthasawat Rd., Lat Phrao, Bangkok 10230 THAILAND', '+666 1929 9225', 'sabai_design@yahoo.com', '+66 2907 7409', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/ador.n.adorn.jewelry', 'https://www.instagram.com/ador.n_adorn', 'ador.n_adorn', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=1LVa1yBitLrFhB0_lRO8Cthe3ULGhS_sR', 'SS19 - The Faith', 'EH 104 : UU -  39, 41, 43', 'In 2015,We had a new fun and exciting project of jewelry design, From the smell project became our proud brand “ADORE’S”\nAdore\'s was founded by two Thai designers,  Paramet Saentaweesuk  and Hasphong Luenloy.\nAdore\'s would like to combine between fine jewelry and fashion. We would talk about the \"Voyage\"\nto discover tribal art and cultures from many places around the world , and use them to inspire our designs for each collection which would bring us and fans of Adore\'s to travel from places to places through our designs.\n', 'This collection,we would bring everybody to travel and explore the spirit of Morocco. The Morocco art,culture and architecture such as the form of exotic roof,delicate pattern on the wall and openings,the shadow on the marble and tiled Floor,and the sky. Everything is our inspiration of this collection telling through the shape,line,materials such as pink gold and opal-the exotic stone which has the combination of milky white,sky blue and amber. both materials represent to sunset and sunrise. This collection concept was delivered to our jewelry in the style,we called \"METribe\"by \"Ador.N Adorn', 1, '2018-10-13 13:09:30', NULL),
(57, 'spectacle', 'simonssister', 'SIMONSSISTER', 'Simonssister Co.,Ltd.', '22/77 Jwgrandta-ra Samwa Rd., Minburi, Bangkok 10510 THAILAND', '+668 9742 6669', 'meladacharonying@gmail.com', '', '', 'www.facebook.com/houseofsimonssister', 'www.instagram.com/simonssisterofficial', 'meladacharonying', '', 'SS19-What is art? What is beauty?', 'EH 100 : X - 16', 'Founded by Miss Melada Ch. and Mr. Chatuphon P. creates the ordinary extraordinary the street-resort wear base in Thailand in 2011.Our collections have a relaxed feel,craftsmanship and and creativity in speacially prints.All print made by our original panting creates by the founder themselves.', 'What is art? What is beauty?....', 1, '2018-10-13 13:09:30', NULL),
